org.pepstock.charba.client.controllers

Class ControllerType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.controllers.ControllerType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Key, Type

    public final class ControllerType
extends Object
implements Type
    Represent the type of new controller. Must be created for every controller implementation.
    It can be created extending an existing chart type or new type.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
